  {
    "id": "tangier",
    "name": "Tangier",
    "description": "Tangier is where Africa meets Europe — a bohemian port city with a legendary medina, stunning Mediterranean views, and a rich literary and artistic heritage that has inspired writers and painters for centuries.",
